    "18": {
      "answer": "The organization you’re looking for is OWASP, or the Open Web Application Security. Their Top 10 list serves as a guide for developers and security teams, helping to prioritize which web vulnerabilities to fix first  and to keep their applications safe from the most common attacks. Two of the current heavy hitters in the top three are broken access control and cryptographic failures.",
